            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">I have an immediate requirement opening for a <strong><font style="background-color: #ffff00">Jr. </font><span style="background: yellow"><font style="background-color: #ffff00">QA</font> Tester position in Ann Arbor, MI. This is a Long term contract position</span></strong>. I would appreciate if you could send your updated word format resume along with best contact details ASAP.</span></div>
