            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Moderately routine; general policies applied. Some decision-making.</span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Education: </span></u></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree from a four year college or university in computer science, management of information services or a related field</span></div>
